                        <td class="py-4 px-6 text-red-400">Continuous (bugs, scaling, patches)</td>
                        <td class="py-4 px-6 text-green-400 font-medium">Managed by Hook0</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
                        <td class="py-4 px-6 text-gray-300">Retry logic</td>
